{"tid":357240,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PS4 Fifa Pro Club] Spring Pocket 為參加更多比賽擴軍，現正招人","createTime":"2017-08-12T16:39:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-22T14:20:56.000Z","uid":4039,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"631525d51f9ae249bc5272a29a9e20ae68cf4b29","tid":357240,"uid":4039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T16:39:37.000Z","msg":"Spring Pocket 經過左兩屆 HKVPL 之後，現今為左擴大規模，為參加更多比賽及迎接 Fifa 18 而於各位置上招納熱愛 pro club 既各位！<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">簡介</span></ins></strong></div><br />\n－參加左近兩屆 HKVPL，順利 o係小組賽進軍金盃賽<br />\n－與其話勁唔勁，不如話我地勝在有一團火<br />\n－我地球隊希望黎緊除左HKVPL 外，再參加其他比賽，所以會盡可能招多d人，等大家shift 下打唔同既比賽<br />\n<br />\n經過兩屆 HKVPL 後，決定為擴大球隊規模。依家我地誠邀各位有心人加入我地！<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">基本條件</span></ins></strong></div><br />\n1. 我地開波時間係大約每日22300-0130<br />\n2. 我地希望搵既係full time<br />\n3. 正式入隊前會試下腳<br />\n4. 主要打地面進攻，節奏唔會太快，習慣傳多幾腳搵多d 機會先<br />\n5. 人仔rating 唔重要，試腳自有分曉<br />\n6. 我地打波慣左開咪提下波，希望大家唔會覺得有壓力<br />\n7. 依家咩野位都收人！<br />\n<br />\n有興趣既球員請經<strong>telegram 聯絡 @sprmanager</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">*為節省問大家問題既時間，請o係telegram 我時提供以下資料：<br />\n<br />\n1. Name:<br />\n2. PSN:<br />\n3. Best Position (ONE only):<br />\n4. Alternatives (1-3 max):<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"95db5d97feaff47ec96e24f06f6e4d4933fcc0d1","tid":357240,"uid":4039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T16:54:17.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4f4e68b1b67848d29127c0806a69bd6fbb5c0574","tid":357240,"uid":4039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T17:08:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"beaf8a9bd366a8fb32c195f18e05175081b12c12","tid":357240,"uid":4039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T18:30:22.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6e10875b11951459d055f9677995d555d49564f2","tid":357240,"uid":4039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score